CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 17, 1962, page 1, reads: "Aims Toward Democracy - Dr. Wade Wilson of Cheyney State Teachers College is shown addressing West Mifflin School Board members, to tell them that the school system needs Negro teachers to further the democratic idea. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Dr. Wade Wilson of Cheyney State Teachers College, standing before men from the West Mifflin School Board, and reporter George Barbour seated around table with documents, in office with TWA calendar on wall, another version
